    <profile id="f2b5-96e3-b094-ef69" name=".50 cal Carrier" typeId="5cbd-556d-67b5-1bd9" typeName="Command Card" hidden="false">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Details" typeId="4091-e11a-c858-f46e">Universal Carriers in this Universal Carrier Patrol lose their normal Universal Carrier (MGs) weapon and gain the following weapon:
WeaponRangeROF HaltedROF MovingAnti- tankFire- 

power
.50 cal MG20&quot;/50cm3245+
.50 cal MGs have the Self-defence AA rule.Self-defence AA: Weapon can Shoot at Aircraft with ROF .</characteristic>
