      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Details" typeId="4091-e11a-c858-f46e">This Unit passes Blitz Move Orders on a 3+.Tank Teams hit by this Formation Commander&apos;s tank must re-roll their successful armour saves.</characteristic>
