      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Details" typeId="4091-e11a-c858-f46e">Add one captured Sd Kfz 10/4 (2cm) to this Unit from a German Sd Kfz 10/4 Light AA Platoon (LG142) with the following rating changes:
